            "id": 6411686,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲2.61%，報47800.34點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間08日09:30，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲1215.88點（或2.61%），暫報47800.34點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.52%</li><li>近 1 月：-1.93%</li><li>近 3 月：-4.92%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.04%</li><li>今年以來：-3.08%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)領漲。聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)上漲9.37%；雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)上漲1.35%；摩根大通銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JPM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JPM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JPM-US</a>)上漲0.66%；亞馬遜(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)上漲0.46%；卡特彼勒(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CAT-US</a>)上漲0.44%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，沃爾瑪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WMT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WMT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WMT-US</a>)下跌3.39%；耐吉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NKE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NKE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NKE-US</a>)下跌3.04%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)下跌2.41%；蘋果(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>)下跌2.07%；漢威聯合國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HON-US</a>)下跌1.91%。</p></section></main>",
